# 🌐 Portfolio Website

A sleek, responsive personal portfolio built with React and Tailwind CSS.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- React
- Tailwind CSS
- JavaScript (ES6+)
- Vite or Create React App

## 📂 Project Structure
- `public/`: Static assets
- `src/components/`: Reusable components
- `src/pages/`: Page components

## 🚀 Getting Started
```bash
npm install
npm run dev
```

## 📸 Features
- Responsive design
- Dark mode toggle
- Animated UI components

